be stereotypes....?

I, too, may be generalizing, but it seems like, in my all-too-brief
experience with this human life, that the real difference between boys and
girls is not what's between their ears, so to speak....

Oh well, back to my PATIENT pursuit of the ultimate light source.....

Nancy


