J. Michael Straczynski has said that his story arc is built to withstand
the departure of any major character. For example, the Talia incident
which caused her departure, was originally planned for Takahashi, the
female C&C officer from the pilot. Takahashi didn't make it to the
regular series, so JMS adapted. (IMHO, it made much more sense, and was
