@{b}From:@{ub}         @{" Stephen G.  " link from 0062} @{i}<sgiff@AIRMAIL.NET> @{ui}
@{b}Subject:@{ub}      @{"Re: Imagine Book" link subj 0869}
---
@{i}>Ok Imagineers (those of you who sent in your checks and showed
@{ui}@{i}>interest), sorry to say that the book will not be completed due to the
@{ui}@{i}>low demand.  After our last post we only received 2 (yes two) checks.
