 PSJ> Has anyone got, or does anyone know where I may find, a good model
 PSJ> of the
 PSJ> Enterprise NCC-1701C? I have found a really good one of 'A' and one
 PSJ> of
 PSJ> 'D', but I would really like 'C' so I can put an anim together.

The Orginal TV enterprise was NCC-1701
The movie version (STTMP) was NCC-1701A
The next generation had an enterprise with 3 naceles (engines) as NCC-1701B
*
The next generation movie shows an "Excelsor" class as NCC-1701C
The next generation (STTNG) was NCC-1701D

*Note the show this appears in is Yesterdays Enterprise (I think). It was
the usual story line of an alternate dimension/reality or dudes from a
future which may or may not happen. This means that this may or may not be
the 'real' "B"


Now my question: I have the A and the D, but have not found the orginal
from the TV show. Is this available?


