---
You have been removed from the Imagine Mailing as a warning for for sending
uuencodes or files through the list.  The charter clearly states that users
are not to send files through the list as they may contain Copyrighted
material.

You may resubscribe to the list by sending a message to
listserv@sjuvm.stjohns.edu
with the body of the message Subscribe Imagine.  If you continue to send files
to the list after this point, you will be locked out of the list permanently.

--Perry Lucas
  Imagine Mailing List Owner


