I just found in my local newsagents. It's called Computer Generated
Imaging and sells for GBP3.95 and is bimonthly.
The first issue has general news articles, test reports on QuickTime VR,
Sculpt 3D,SoftFX,3D Studio,Truespace 2.0, lots of pictures and a feature
on the graphics effects in the file Babe. There's other stuff too. There
are ads for Viewpoint,Raydream, Softimage etc. Anyone that's interested
the address is:
