Louis Sinclair wrote a VERY NICE (!!) tutorial on how to continue (sort of) an
interrupted rendering (by flipping the camera or by blocking the view and
then merging the new picture with the old disrupted one).

There is however a very simple way of accomlishing the same result:
Set Zone.

