By the way, what the heck should I use to view your
@{i}>anims?  They just sparkle shades of blue and I can barely make out whats
@{ui}@{i}>happening.
@{ui}
Just make a project in Imagine, then a subproject, and move the file you want to
see into that subproject. Open the project, load the subproject, and load the
anim. Then play!

PS.One anim at the time, you cant have two anim files in the same subproject
dir.

Tom


