@{i}> Hi, I'd like to make a few questions to the community.
@{ui}@{i}>
@{ui}@{i}> I'm new in this business, and I need advice on what to do with my machine.
@{ui}@{i}> First of all, I have to tell you that there's no Amiga dealer here in Uruguay,
