@{ui}@{i}>
@{ui}@{i}> 1) Wait untill escom launches the PowerAmiga.
@{ui}@{i}> 2) Get a PC version for my 486 DX266.
@{ui}@{i}> 3) Get an accelerator board.
@{ui}@{i}> 4) Get just a FPU.
@{ui}@{i}> 5) Start learning Imagine with the machine I have and decide only when I think
@{ui}@{i}> I need more machine to do more things.
