I'd suggest #5, at least for now, as a universal solution. You may not be
able to use a lot of the textures, and you may not have enough RAM for
the truly massive projects, but all this frees you from worrying about
the complicated stuff. I'd say wait and see. But, I must admit, I'm
personally going for option #1. =)

