On Mon, 12 Feb 1996 Margaret Copeland wrote:
@{i}>>>BTW, does anyone know of a PD Amiga utility that can format a Syquest
@{ui}cartridge as a PCDos cartridge? Does CrossDos do this now ?<<<

I did this once many moons ago. CrossPC was able to do it, but it required a
working copy of MS-DOS on a floppy. It's a little complicated though. It might
be simpler just to take the Syquest to the service bureau (or friend with PC and
Syquest), and have them format it for you. Once the disk is formatted CrossDOS
should recognize it, I believe.

