Minimum investment, minimum speed, depending on the accelerator. Could cost
almost as much as option (2)

@{i}>5) Start learning Imagine with the machine I have and decide only when I think
@{ui}@{i}>I need more machine to do more things.
@{ui}
Depends on the level of technolust you suffer from! Waiting for renders could
get painfull. If you've got thwe money ($200 US), I'd go for option (2)

Bill B


