If someone will create a short, to-the-point *newbie* faq which covers IN
DEPTH all facets of making Imagine run on a PC, then I'll be happy, and
maybe just a few of my fellow newbies will have a USEFUL source of info.

Sorry for the close-to-off-topic, but this has really been buggiong me for
