---
To all the newbies who have joined us (and anyone else interested), I
have a tutorial on my ftp site. This tut involves modeling, bones, IK,
states, and animation. It is written with the new user in mind. Although
it uses a few version 4 tools, 3 users should be able to work around. In
case of trouble, models from different stages of completion are
included.
Download mantut.zip from:

ftp://users.aol.com/valleyview/imagine/

AOL posts a lot of garbage first, so scroll to the bottom.
Hope this helps get you started.

Rick


