@node 0575 "Message number 0575"

@{b}Date:@{ub}         @{"Thu, 15 Feb 1996 18:21:21 +0100 " link day.15 }
@{b}From:@{ub}         @{"Per Sverre Wold-Hansen " link from 1075} @{i}<woldh@MOTHER.NORCONNECT.NO> @{ui}
@{b}Subject:@{ub}      @{"Re: Light and shadows" link subj 0975}
---
@{i}>I have created a scene with a series of columns in a semi-circle
@{ui}@{i}>and a glowing orb at the centre of the circle. The glowing orb has
@{ui}@{i}>got an axis that I made a light source (L1) positioned at its centre.
@{ui}@{i}>Also placed in the scene is another light source (L2) of the the right
@{ui}@{i}>side of the camera, this light was placed in the stage editor.
@{ui}@{i}>refer to ascii diagram below.
@{ui}
@{i}>                             o
@{ui}@{i}>                          o     o
@{ui}@{i}>                        o    L1   o
@{ui}@{i}>                       o           o
@{ui}
@{i}>                                             L2
@{ui}

@{i}>                             \/
@{ui}@{i}>                           camera
@{ui}
@{i}>L1 and L2 are both lights of diminishing intesity with the same intesity
@{ui}@{i}>values, L2 is the only shadow casting light source.
@{ui}
@{i}>Initially I ray-traced the scene only using the Light L1, I then added
@{ui}@{i}>L2 but when the ray trace was complete the shadows from L2 had darkened
@{ui}@{i}>the surfaces that had previously been fully illuminated by L1.
@{ui}
@{i}>What is going on, if L2 was of greater intensity than L1 you should be able
@{ui}@{i}>to see shadows, but the shadows cast by L2 should not darken areas
@{ui}@{i}>that are illuminated by L1.
@{ui}
@{i}>Stuart Fletcher
@{ui}
Sounds to me as if L1 is shadowcasting.

If Imagine itself isn't playing a trick on us, I would assume
that you also have made L1 shadowcasting after adding L2. In THAT
case, if no light can escape from the orb you're describing -
no light will hit the columns in trace mode.

OR - Did you REALLY _trace_ your first try - Shure it wasn't scanline?
No account is taken for shadowcasting when in scanline'ing.

     ** Per Sverre **
    Fredrikstad Norway
     woldh@sirius.no


			@{"   Return  to  Main    " link main}
			@{"Return to Natural Index" link natural}
@endnode
