So I had to resort to Lightwave - Took some time to master, but
I DID get my wonderful myriad of dancing and flaring electrons
inside a tube.

I've gladly jumped back on to Imagine - But when do we get decent
lensflares here?

In my opinion this represents one of Imagine's MAJOR deficiencies!

A full session on SIGGRAPH '96 was devoted to this topic,
with numerous references, so the logic and algorithms
should be easily accessible.


