---
On Fri, 16 Feb 1996 17:18:33 -0500  Nancy Jacobs wrote:
@{i}>BTW, do you know of any good CHEAP (shareware, maybe) CAD progs that have
@{ui}@{i}>some useful tools (including decent bezier curves) and outputs a reasonable
@{ui}@{i}>dxf file ?
