other low-cost poly-programs to see if there are any decent reduction or
optimization routines. I haven't examined these recently, so I can't say
what's out there.
This is also something that would make a nice .IFX modeling procedural, if
someone had the inclination. Let me see what Alfonso Hermida has to say.

If your goal is principally to speed up rendering though, there may be
other things that can be done about that.

