@{b}Date:@{ub}         @{"Sun, 18 Feb 1996 02:05:45 -0500 " link day.18 }
@{b}From:@{ub}         @{"Paul Frey " link from 1070} @{i}<Postvideo@AOL.COM> @{ui}
@{b}Subject:@{ub}      @{"Hello" link subj 0255}
---
Hello Imagineers!
My name is Paul Frey.
I am Senior Systems Analyst who would rather be drawing, modeling and
animating.
A friend and I started a small political cartoon and clipart company called
Our World Comics.
