Alfonso Hermida wrote:
@{i}>
@{ui}@{i}> Hello:
@{ui}@{i}>         I'm Alfonso Hermida and this is my first message on the Imagine
@{ui} mailing
@{i}> list.  Tim Wilson suggested I hook up with the list and here I am.
@{ui}@{i}>
@{ui}@{i}>         I'm currently working on a routine to do fracturing/smoothing of
