@{i}>>>it would be interesting to hear why you set up your buttons the way you
@{ui}did<<<
        I can't remember hot keys for one thing. The buttons are the ones I use
most frequently. I like to have modal commands as gadgets, so I can tell whether
I'm in Pick Point, Pick Group, Drag Box mode, etc. at a glance. Then I've got
buttons to adjust the perspective view, in particular to switch between the New
Mode perspective and Shaded mode, and I just recently added a button for Make
Quick Edges, so I can update this as I'm adding new faces, and rotate my full
geometry in realtime.

