@{ui}@{i}> Pentium with Windhose95 and I have used PC's at my job for several years.
@{ui}@{i}> I even remember using Windoze 1 on a real IBM 8086 PC.
@{ui}@{i}>   And I have looked high and low for any DOS/Win paint and animation
