Anders Lundholm wrote:
@{i}>  Considering the things people on this list are doing on low-end systems
@{ui}@{i}> like 486's and 040\060's I'm more than sure that scenarios created using an
@{ui}@{i}> Indigo^2 High Impact will make great impact in both game industries and
