Chuck metioned Tim W's solution (globes), but didn't provide it. It was :
Use the image map twice at 180 degrees to each other and use
subgroups to restrict them. One of the maps needs to be "wrapped"
halfway around in a paint program. You'll work it out. Should be
a similar trick for tiles.
