@{i}>>>When I Have an project open, I whould like to go from Detail editor to scene
@{ui}@{i}>>>editor, widouth loosing the object i'm working on it (sord of lightwave), i
@{ui}@{i}>>>found that it is very annoing to be working  in a object, then go to stage
