First a couple of points:

To the newbie who thought he might not have got all the textures with his
coverdisc version of Imagine. Quite right, you didn't! Print out your copy
of the textures text that came on your coverdisc and compare that with what
you find on your installed copy. Roughly speaking you got about 30 out of 100.

